<FlowDocument>
<Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H2}">Minecraft Live 总结</Paragraph><Paragraph>9 月 28 日凌晨一点，Minecraft Live 公布了下一个小更新的内容</Paragraph><Paragraph><Italic>以下非最终译名，仅供参考</Italic></Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">名称为 《Mounts of Mayhem》</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">加入了 The Nautilus（鹦鹉螺生物），在海中生成，玩家可以喂河豚，使用鞍骑乘穿梭于海底</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">会被河豚吸引</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">在骑乘的时候会有一个状态效果，使得氧气不会消耗</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">可以冲刺</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">有其幼年形态 Baby Nautilus</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">可以装备不同材料制成的 Nautilus Armor（鹦鹉螺甲）</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">有 Zombie Nautilus（僵尸鹦鹉螺）变体，上面会骑乘溺尸</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">加入了 The Spear（矛）武器</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">两根木棍和一个材料左下到右上斜向放置合成</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">可以在前进时攻击敌人</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">普通攻击有 CD（目测1秒）</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">可以充能攻击，在移动时对面前的目标造成伤害</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">攻击伤害受移动速度影响</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">自然可以生成僵尸马了，在僵尸马上会骑乘一个拿着 Spear 的僵尸</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://tc-new.z.wiki/autoupload/f/2c6MK0d62soElBOCIA-_FXmEkftwpfXYFOUOEy8VZ4ayl5f0KlZfm6UsKj-HyTuv/20250928/WPGR/MCV_LIVE_holiday2025_editorial_1170x500.jpg.avif/webp"/></BlockUIContainer><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://tc-new.z.wiki/autoupload/f/2c6MK0d62soElBOCIA-_FXmEkftwpfXYFOUOEy8VZ4ayl5f0KlZfm6UsKj-HyTuv/20250928/LfYj/MCV_holidaydrop2025_LIVE_nautilus_01_1280x720.jpg.avif/webp"/></BlockUIContainer><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://tc-new.z.wiki/autoupload/f/2c6MK0d62soElBOCIA-_FXmEkftwpfXYFOUOEy8VZ4ayl5f0KlZfm6UsKj-HyTuv/20250928/JNp8/MCV_holidaydrop2025_LIVE_nautilus_06_armor_gold_1280x720.jpg.avif/webp"/></BlockUIContainer><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://tc-new.z.wiki/autoupload/f/2c6MK0d62soElBOCIA-_FXmEkftwpfXYFOUOEy8VZ4ayl5f0KlZfm6UsKj-HyTuv/20250928/CdWK/MCV_holidaydrop2025_LIVE_attack_jab_3_1280x720.jpg.avif/webp"/></BlockUIContainer>
